Alpha Dolphy/Starice::

Alpah was very bored since she arrived to MAximal city, she haven't 
done so much since she arrived. So she started work in a device that 
would be abble to cacht Maximal's signals and locate them in a map, 
Alpha located Panzer's signal and she open comm link with Iron Raptor.

"Errrr.... Miss Raptor" said the young femme in all  Maximals' 
frecuencies "I'm Alpha I'm one of Epyon's crew that arrived with 
Starjumper, I caught a Maximal signal in Europe and it's moving to 
East..."

Starice recived the comm link and gave a quick sight to Eyebright, 
she wasn't sure if she should leave her a short while.
